values: My uncle got sick yesterday. .-. My cousins said he was dizzy all week, and when they went to get some water, he was pale, on the floor. he was sent to the hospital. I haven't seen him yet, but he's okay, so yeah. I went to the mall today with my cousin, and saw 2 others. We had fun shopping and talking. I AMS A MULTITASKER. XD I got the second volume of MAR.  8D And I read it in 10 minutes. And I start summer camp tommorw. Well, day camp. We're going to Sandy Hook beach. It's nice and clean and fun. :3 And I get to see my friends I haven't seen n a year. ...I've got to remember to get their numbers and screennames. D:

I went to a friend's b-day, today. :3 We played football, baseball, pinata (I gots a lot of candy :3), water guns, trampoline boxing, and a lot more. Great food. Cake~ I tested a theory I heard about. I took some gum, and started chewing it. Soon, I put some chocolate and started chewing it to. And soon, the chocolate and gum dissolved! XD It was fun~ Although, we did get lost on the way home for 5 minutes.... >.> And we saw this poor roadkill raccoon. ;_; Poor thing. Also, I thank Nuki for hooking me on Foamy the Squirrel. :3

Okay, first post. Nothing special. I gotta get some pretty avatar things. Okay, so today was boring. I stayed home today, got the 3rd Pure Heart in Super Paper Mario today. :3 I went to the park with my cousins. And OMG, it was disgusting! D: There were pigeons and duck and geese and miles and miles of crap everywhere! >_< But, we saw a beaver~  ^o^ And some black girl left her cell phone near us when she went to play. o.o Someone could of stole it! We took it and opened it, but it was off, so we put it back. XD It was fun~ And I have 2 puppies in my lap who are trying to get out of my grip. WELL, I'M NOT LETTING GO YOU CUTE WIDDLE THINGS! >:O
